 1. When the start and end of the existing intervals are the same as the existing intervals, then remove the interval from the list.
 2. If the interval to be deleted lies in the between the existing range, then I am dividing the existing interval into 2 intervals excluding the interval to be deleted &amp; adding the 2 new intervals in the list.
